Friends and family members of veteran actor, Patrick Shai gathered on Saturday to pay their respects at his funeral in Soweto. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Family and friends of veteran actor Patrick Shai gathered on Saturday to pay their respects at his funeral in Soweto. The legendary actor died last weekend. His wife, Mmasechaba Shai, says it has been difficult to express the hurt she is feeling over his passing. She says it is hard to come to terms with his death. WATCH: Funeral service of actor Patrick Shai "This is a message that I never thought I would be saying," she said. "I really can't say goodbye but I can't say goodbye. We have had our laughter, we've had our challenges, we've had so many things that we were dealing with. We had plans." Meanwhile, Shai's children say they will remember their father for his support and jokes, among other things. They have hailed him as their hero.